text: Sanaz Marand and Florencia Molinero were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Laura Siegemund and Renata Voráčová won the title, defeating María Irigoyen and Stephanie Vogt in the final, 6–2, 6–1. == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Internazionali Femminili di Brescia - Doubles
